com.wx.io

Class TextAccessor

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.wx.io.TextAccessor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Closeable, java.lang.AutoCloseable

    public class TextAccessor
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Closeable
    Utility method that regroup all the common stream operations into one class.
    An Accessor can contain up to 2 streams (1 in, 1 out).
